Klopp: &ldquo;I was angry because we wanted to change and we wanted to change the system! The referee didn&rsquo;t give us this opportunity.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;We wanted to change to 5 at the back and I think that could have helped a lot. That&rsquo;s where Willian popped up with the goal.&rdquo;

Klopp: &ldquo;The line-up of Chelsea was obviously for a nice counter-attacking game. That makes it difficult, especially when you see Eden Hazard.&quot;<br />
<br />
