Klopp on Salah: &quot;I love this player but we can&rsquo;t speak all the time after a game about him. He can play in this kind of game as a 9 as well which is good for us.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;I thought it was a good team performance from us in an unbelievably difficult game. Chelsea with 8 players behind the ball.&quot;

Mignolet on Willian's goal: &quot;I think he was looking to try and cross to the far post but the ball breaks perfectly for him.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mignolet: &quot;You try to make up for it and you try to get there in the air but it&rsquo;s just one you have to take.&quot;
